cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.DC 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Science sub-category of Network and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) as it deals with the management and orchestration of virtual network functions. Additionally, the paper proposes a solution based on deep reinforcement learning (DRL), which falls under the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also formulates the problem as a parameterized action Markov decision process (PAMDP), which falls under the sub-category of Control Systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the optimization of resources, which falls under the sub-category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC).
